{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idab50dcf5-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s8868"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"8868"},"text":"§ 8868.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Disposition of prize money","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The net proceeds of all property condemned as prize shall be decreed to the United States and shall be ordered by the court to be paid into the Treasury.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idab50dcf6-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1956-08-10/ch1041"},"text":"Aug. 10, 1956, ch. 1041","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/70A/480"},"text":"70A Stat. 480","children":[],"tail":", § 7668; renumbered § 8868, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/232/dA/tVIII/s807/d/9"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–232, div. A, title VIII, § 807(d)(9)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-08-13"},"text":"Aug. 13, 2018","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/132/1837"},"text":"132 Stat. 1837","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idab50dcf7-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"historicalAndRevision","id":"idab50dcf8-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:table","attrib":{"width":"50%","id":"idab50dcf9-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:colgroup","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:col","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"html:col","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"html:col","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"html:thead","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:tr","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:th","attrib":{"colspan":"3"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:span","attrib":{},"text":"Historical and Revision Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"html:tr","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:th","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:i","attrib":{},"text":"Revised section","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"html:th","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:i","attrib":{},"text":"Source (U.S. Code)","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"html:th","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:i","attrib":{},"text":"Source (Statutes at Large)","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"html:tbody","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:tr","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:td","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:span","attrib":{},"text":"7668","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"html:td","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:a","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t34/s1151"},"text":"34 U.S.C. 1151","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"html:td","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":"R.S. 4630; R.S. 4641.","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"R.S. 4630 provided that in some circumstances the captors were to receive the net proceeds of prize property and in other circumstances they were to receive half and the United States was to receive the other half. The ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1899-03-03/ch413/s13"},"text":"Act of March 3, 1899, ch. 413, § 13","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/30/1007"},"text":"30 Stat. 1007","children":[],"tail":", repealed “all provisions of law authorizing the distribution among captors of the whole or any portion of the proceeds of vessels, or any property hereafter captured, condemned as prize”. Thus the only part of R.S. 4630 that remains in effect, as is indicated in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t34/s1151"},"text":"34 U.S.C. 1151","children":[],"tail":", is that part which provides that proceeds shall be decreed to the United States. The section is so worded. R.S. 4641 stated how proceeds decreed to captors should be divided among them. These provisions were eliminated by the Act of "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1899-03-03"},"text":"March 3, 1899","children":[],"tail":", supra. All that remains of R.S. 4641, as is indicated in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t34/s1151"},"text":"34 U.S.C. 1151","children":[],"tail":", is the provision that proceeds decreed to the United States shall be paid into the Treasury, and the section is worded accordingly."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idab50dcfa-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idab50dcfb-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2018—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/232"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–232","children":[],"tail":" renumbered "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s7668"},"text":"section 7668 of this title","children":[],"tail":" as this section."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idab50dcfc-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"idab50dcfd-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2018 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/232"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–232","children":[],"tail":" effective "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2019-02-01"},"text":"Feb. 1, 2019","children":[],"tail":", with provision for the coordination of amendments and special rule for certain redesignations, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/232/s800"},"text":"section 800 of Pub. L. 115–232","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note preceding "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s3001"},"text":"section 3001 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
